    {
      "id": "44b45a57-f894-4141-bbe2-05e1e316803c",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit~$E$ l'ensemble des fonctions $f : \\R \\to \\R$ de classe $\\mathcal{C}^\\infty$\ntelle que pour tout~$k\\in\\N$, $f^{(k)}$ est bornée.\n\nSoit $u : E \\to E, f \\mapsto {f+f'.}$",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(E\\)</span> l’ensemble des fonctions <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f : \\R \\to \\R\\)</span> de classe <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{C}^\\infty\\)</span> telle que pour tout <span class=\"math inline\">\\(k\\in\\N\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f^{(k)}\\)</span> est bornée.</p>\n<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(u : E \\to E, f \\mapsto {f+f&#39;.}\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "65ea33a1-5cdd-424b-a3d9-9ef6c3c80b22",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $u\\in\\mathcal{L}(E)$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(u\\in\\mathcal{L}(E)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7548a68f-5fd6-419f-8cb9-6734998a4e81",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Est-ce que~$u$ est injectif~?",
        "html": "<p>Est-ce que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(u\\)</span> est injectif ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "a49bcb6f-afc0-44bc-bc5c-6b27046f945f",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Est-ce que~$u$ est surjectif~?",
        "html": "<p>Est-ce que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(u\\)</span> est surjectif ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f005ac3b-5b93-40fc-80a4-c3cd87f36667",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Oui, $\\mathrm{Ker} u = \\{0\\}$.\nOui~: si $g\\in E$ alors $f = t \\mapsto \\int_{s=-\\infty}^t e^{s-t}g(s)\\,d s$\n    appartient~à~$E$ et $f+f'=g$.",
        "html": "<p>Oui, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathrm{Ker} u = \\{0\\}\\)</span>. Oui : si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(g\\in E\\)</span> alors <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f = t \\mapsto \\int_{s=-\\infty}^t e^{s-t}g(s)\\,d s\\)</span> appartient à <span class=\"math inline\">\\(E\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f+f&#39;=g\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
}